title: BABYMETAL - Discography and Videography
description:
OK Don't ask me why I uploaded this but for some unexplainable hypnotic reason I just 
could'nt resist.
A JPOP/Death Metal Band with adorable Japanese girls singing and dancing about.
I think it's Japans secret weapon to take over the world.
But on a serious note I find them interesting and of course i'm a sucker
for any kind of Female Fronted Metal although this is slightly different.
Like Britney Spears singing with Kataklysm or Cannibal Corpse and
making it.....cute?....for lack of a better term.
Anyway please SEED and enjoy this captivating enigma known as BABYMETAL.

Quality is mostly 720p for the Videos 

and 320kbps for the Music


Pitufo7777
